449
00:19:47,230 --> 00:19:48,230
But you were the one

450
00:19:48,230 --> 00:19:51,050
who killed my friend's
family, that right?

451
00:19:51,050 --> 00:19:52,220
Eiji's family, I mean.

452
00:19:52,220 --> 00:19:53,260
(gasping)

453
00:19:53,260 --> 00:19:55,130
Senkaku!

454
00:19:55,130 --> 00:19:56,190
Huh?

455
00:19:56,190 --> 00:19:58,280
♪

456
00:19:58,280 --> 00:20:00,030
I knew from the
very beginning

457
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:02,240
that you wouldn't be able
to beat Kenshin Himura.

458
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:04,120
But if you lose
without forcing him

459
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:06,150
