462
00:20:11,190 --> 00:20:14,280
(grunting)

463
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:19,280
♪

464
00:20:19,280 --> 00:20:21,130
-Through there?
-Yeah.

465
00:20:21,130 --> 00:20:23,110
-No, ahh!
-Thank you!

466
00:20:23,110 --> 00:20:24,070
Careful, Eiji,

467
00:20:24,070 --> 00:20:25,270
we've got to
be super quiet.

468
00:20:25,270 --> 00:20:27,130
♪

469
00:20:27,130 --> 00:20:29,200
(gasping)

470
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:32,090
Hiten Mitsurugi style.

471
00:20:32,090 --> 00:20:33,200
(speaking foreign language)

472
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:35,260
(grunting)

473
00:20:35,260 --> 00:20:38,050
(yelling)

474
00:20:38,050 --> 00:20:39,180
(thudding)

475
00:20:39,180 --> 00:20:42,260
(gasping)

476
00:20:42,260 --> 00:20:44,060
Do you see that?

477
00:20:44,060 --> 00:20:45,070
Nice move.

478
00:20:45,070 --> 00:20:46,150
Amazing.

479
00:20:46,150 --> 00:20:48,120
(gasping)

480
00:20:50,170 --> 00:20:51,200
Why did you
leave him alive?

481
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:53,190
He would've killed
you if he could have.

482
00:20:53,190 --> 00:20:55,290
Someday showing mercy
