blood for any reason.

484
00:20:59,190 --> 00:21:01,150
It doesn't serve
any purpose.

485
00:21:01,150 --> 00:21:02,260
True.

486
00:21:02,260 --> 00:21:04,150
But it can be amusing.

487
00:21:04,150 --> 00:21:15,040
♪

488
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:16,210
Shishio.

